data.description: Charming Ranch home on almost 1/2 an acre with welcoming rocking chair front porch.  Tucked away on this quiet dead end street, this well-maintained property is bright, cheery, and move-in ready. Enjoy the spacious kitchen, cozy living room with fireplace, and bonus private screened in back porch that overlooks the beautiful backyard with tons of room for outdoor activities. Real Hardwood floors and new paint throughout main living area and most of house. Oversized primary bedroom has separate his and hers closets! New carpet in primary and 2nd bedroom. Two-car carport and long driveway provide plenty of parking on the level front lot. Downstairs crawl space has window, partial slab and offers many creative opportunities for use beyond storage. Great location, only 5 minutes from the popular Jaemor Farms and 20 minutes from downtown Gainesville!
